I was thinking on this, and whats really silly is that you can already server transfer all droppable items, its just it requires hopping you char onto storm hammer, transfering items to a new stormhammer char you just made, then transferring your new char to target server (free) and doing a normal transfer for your original char.<br>
<br>
So you can already move tradeables.<br>
<br>
Worrying about moving no drops which can't affect economies is laughable in light of that. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://homepages.nildram.co.uk/~dharman/CassiusRuneblaze.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
